titocc.compiler.elements

Class Function

  • java.lang.Object
    • titocc.compiler.elements.CodeElement
      • titocc.compiler.elements.Declaration
        • titocc.compiler.elements.Function
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Symbol

    public class Function
extends Declaration
implements Symbol
    Function declaration and definition. Forward declarations are not currently supported so this is always both declaration and definition. Functions consist of return type, function name, parameter list and a BlockStatement body.

    EBNF definition:
    FUNCTION = TYPE_SPECIFIER IDENTIFIER PARAMETER_LIST BLOCK_STATEMENT
